{"tid":1272034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"身為一個黃絲但屋企人係深藍既我想對未有經濟能力卻同有同樣處境既青少年講番說話","createTime":"2019-07-01T08:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T18:32:38.000Z","uid":3209,"like":1344,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3e72dc4933a6a4e7f2eaefb4eed8a636f7d51a","tid":1272034,"uid":3209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"我係一個大學生 番下part time 一個月都有$3000-5000既收入 但明顯係香港生活係完全唔夠<br />\n我老豆係深藍 即使我俾曬證據咁講曬成件事 佢都係支持警察 支持政府 <br />\n當下當然好嬲 好想立即搬走<br />\n但我諗一諗 點解我唔食佢住佢等佢繼續供書教學 等我有時間空間資源努力成材 等有一日我由一粒small potato 變成big potato既時候我再一獲撬起佢？<br />\n我身為一個乞食科垃圾 歷史教訓咗我要成事之前 一需要忍，二需要等<br />\n你食佢地住佢地洗佢地錢 一樣可以遊行 甚至用佢俾你d錢幫助義士買物資（我做緊)<br />\n但你自己同時繼續有時間空間資源去進修自己<br />\n講真 你想救香港 做一個有say有資源既人先可以做出更大貢獻<br />\n「成大事者，不佝小節也」佢地罵你係你面前隔住電視罵義士們 我明白你好嬲 我都好嬲<br />\n但你更應該將依種悲憤令自己頭腦更清醒<br />\n明白利用敵人手上既資源達成我地自己既目標先係上策 我唔知大家點諗<br />\n但我唔希望今日既義士 他朝需要遊行完番m記開工<br />\n如果你好有錢既話咁你當冇睇過<br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"8191c6872cf6fb5b3bc406974214015744d83288","tid":1272034,"uid":79611,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:45:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eccdec7aca9670e4fcf451dc71676b7446481285","tid":1272034,"uid":108337,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"沉默是你的朋友"},{"pid":"31cb0580381f4222f69646a903feee880643ea95","tid":1272034,"uid":3209,"like":386,"dislike":1,"score":385,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"我中學個時撞正雨傘上過街 到屋企人撐到行<br />\n結果發現自己既弱小同無力<br />\n個刻開始我要好好利用藍絲屋企人既資源<br />\n去成就自己 再用自己資源回饋香港<br />\n大家千其唔好俾憤怒沖擊自己<br />\n越嬲 你越應該冷靜 諗下點樣係敵人身上榨取利益去達成自己目的<br />\n甚至我依家唔同佢傾政治 扮到好政治冷感咁<br />\n做個樣俾佢地睇 放低佢地戒心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce734dd6f849dc8d08bdf6010c865e5ec9ee965","tid":1272034,"uid":55056,"like":240,"dislike":7,"score":233,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"我一直有個異曲同工既睇法<br />\n以前見朋友同學呃政府屋 呃資助 假離婚 覺得好不屑 <br />\n依家覺得咁做先係還富於民 將資源重新回收有效利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df481a0c7c86a3adac1a0775ddfaf1d3d1ccc95","tid":1272034,"uid":45320,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:59:16.000Z","msg":"「臥薪嘗膽」用來形容一個人忍辱負重，發憤圖強，終能夠苦盡甘來。"},{"pid":"235be4c31c25b28cadcb2d0de12bb44c7bd777c8","tid":1272034,"uid":3209,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"quote":{"pid":"cce734dd6f849dc8d08bdf6010c865e5ec9ee965","tid":1272034,"uid":55056,"like":240,"dislike":7,"score":233,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"我一直有個異曲同工既睇法<br />\n以前見朋友同學呃政府屋 呃資助 假離婚 覺得好不屑 <br />\n依家覺得咁做先係還富於民 將資源重新回收有效利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"唔努力還唔努力 唔好將懶變成理由<br />\n養佢地同養大陸新移民冇咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d38be632739305f47639a00fe94d5112a94b09","tid":1272034,"uid":192068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd173945ca41726ebd8739efe20efce9096f014","tid":1272034,"uid":6548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"放心 佢地最怕冇仔送終 佢地一定會受返"},{"pid":"323fa2cb85146429448dc1a0f9f601018c27cfa9","tid":1272034,"uid":225564,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:04:17.000Z","msg":"這個世有一日會係我地呢一代嘅"},{"pid":"23d7df991c1a92a2f9d817484850129fd1a2cb01","tid":1272034,"uid":6548,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"5dd173945ca41726ebd8739efe20efce9096f014","tid":1272034,"uid":6548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"放心 佢地最怕冇仔送終 佢地一定會受返"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"一邊食佢資源一係等機會唔認佢地"},{"pid":"bf5e9f3f609579943cd36813ba48466e1b82f073","tid":1272034,"uid":6548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>放心 佢地最怕冇仔送終 佢地一定會受返</blockquote>一邊食佢資源一邊等機會唔認佢地</blockquote>"},{"pid":"dfe92d2498162a976892131948658df34b6a7645","tid":1272034,"uid":3209,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"323fa2cb85146429448dc1a0f9f601018c27cfa9","tid":1272034,"uid":225564,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:04:17.000Z","msg":"這個世有一日會係我地呢一代嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:06:08.000Z","msg":"岩 等佢地死曬個一日就得<br />\n我地依家要做既係世界仔<br />\n一方面係佢地面前扮野 另一方面做我地應該要做既事"},{"pid":"3eb1f6a634a6516ce462499db9342b3a1b81744f","tid":1272034,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:06:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c66eab1c70cb15bceb948a91a8888554c1b87fbc","tid":1272034,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:06:57.000Z","msg":"好post"},{"pid":"0461fbc1a0e893f3778d9de9a94500995e4be294","tid":1272034,"uid":76632,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:11:25.000Z","msg":"將來唔好俾藍絲家人知道你有幾多收入，盡量唔好俾太多家用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OHmVhMK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOHmVhMK.jpg&h=1af1b1f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c86079973f8d41089323bacd6179653473184e4","tid":1272034,"uid":12533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:12:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5054d8b7b6c801c43d66b07ecce4d81630e2be2e","tid":1272034,"uid":225564,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"永遠唔好忘記 自己期待嘅世界<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得 司法要透明 上網要自由 樓價要同收入有一定比例"},{"pid":"3ddd5210d230634d48d02e25b47d9d021be0720f","tid":1272034,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:16:32.000Z","msg":"奉勸一句<br />\n勿以硬碰硬<br />\n<br />\n上計投本土泛民<br />\n下計一齊旅行"},{"pid":"01be5a98a99be5ad23f76f32143a886cf83c3873","tid":1272034,"uid":218002,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:18:07.000Z","msg":"借個位放下負<br />\n岩岩同老母嘈完都好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢仲話我無良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為左政治同佢嘈<br />\n我已經為左唔同佢嘈味住良心唔去遊行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就黎出去做野 第日移民咪得 <br />\n唔洗逼到自己咁辛苦<br />\n但有無人明白戈種唔捨得屋企變成咁既心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b193d81bc927e6b8078b74935e4eee37daf2891d","tid":1272034,"uid":241101,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:20:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1272003/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1272003/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n林夕：鬥長命 1-7-2019<br />\n<br />\n今日，乃香港回歸週年紀念，實在太值得紀念。<br />\n<br />\n要記錄與念及這二十二年，香港是如何一步步變得陌生。<br />\n<br />\n要紀念以前遊行示威還沒有成為風土病的日子。<br />\n<br />\n要紀念基本法與中英聯合聲明已成任意刪改燒毀的殘骸。<br />\n<br />\n要記錄所有被權力腐化了的人形喪屍，講的不是人話。<br />\n<br />\n要記住香港有防止被喪屍感染的權利，要講良心話。<br />\n<br />\n要紀念今年回歸盛典的升旗禮，取消了學生參與的資格，這個口口聲聲說重視年輕人的政府，重視的意思，原來就是防範學生，害怕還有血性的年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n要記錄這個政權的冷漠與傲慢，香港人犯了什麼錯，會有如此不堪的遭遇。每念及首長的嘴臉，生氣之後就是難過。我們的訴求，從第一天起步爭取開始，就明白越惡的法越容易過，越善良的人心裏越不好過。<br />\n<br />\n正是因為不好過，才不會像喪屍般失去了正常人會有的情緒：激動、傷心、流淚、忿忿不平。一個人在情緒高漲或低落的時候，別做出重大的決定，這是很多人說過的道理，但沒有這種衝動，就像許多自詡冷靜高明的旁觀者一樣，永遠不會有行動。不過，行動是因為有想法，有想法的話，也必然會思考，衝動之時，別讓感性蓋過理性。<br />\n<br />\n有血有肉的人，絕不會輕易投降，所以，更不要為喪屍沒人性，而犧牲人命，不值得。走在抗爭的路上，一個都不能少，二百萬加一、加二，那個可悲的尾數，一個都不能再多了。<br />\n<br />\n我們不會相信明天會更好這種自我安慰的麻醉劑，但絕對有條件相信明天的明天的明天，腐化的高牆必有腐爛倒下的一日。我們不會坐着等，而是站出來行出來。<br />\n<br />\n我們已經從外殼脆弱易碎的雞蛋，蛻變成子彈打不破的水。細水長流，才會無堅不摧，一時間被困在水塔，終會讓坐在塔尖的人倒下來。<br />\n<br />\n懷着赤子之心的人，還沒有天真到幻想一步登天，堅持的代價就是耐性耐力。在對的路上，偶然也會犯錯，路程也特別漫長，會沮喪會失望，只要站在公義這一邊，就唔需要計較一時的得失。水無常形，不義的政權更比人生無常。<br />\n<br />\n我們付出所有力量，每次失敗其實都在培養更持久的能量。<br />\n<br />\n紀念回歸，要相信念念不忘，必有迴響；要保持力量，就要鬥命長。<br />\n<br />\n「走上不獻媚的路，腳步注定緩慢。」<br />\n<br />\n所以，要和喪屍鬥命長。 <br />\n<br />\n林夕 <br />\n電郵 :linxiapple@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n原文link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%95/daily/article/20190701/20717048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%2595%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F20717048&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=e97da230\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%2595%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F20717048&h=3a16201a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%95/daily/article/20190701/20717048</a>"},{"pid":"fcef61115dc79d89b39245df2364fec055360e3d","tid":1272034,"uid":3209,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"01be5a98a99be5ad23f76f32143a886cf83c3873","tid":1272034,"uid":218002,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:18:07.000Z","msg":"借個位放下負<br />\n岩岩同老母嘈完都好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢仲話我無良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為左政治同佢嘈<br />\n我已經為左唔同佢嘈味住良心唔去遊行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就黎出去做野 第日移民咪得 <br />\n唔洗逼到自己咁辛苦<br />\n但有無人明白戈種唔捨得屋企變成咁既心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:25:51.000Z","msg":"你咪順下老母把口 跟住照出去遊行 <br />\n遊行完番屋企餐飽飯<br />\n第二日先有力繼續遊行同做野<br />\n好過你為啖氣飯又冇得食 遊行又冇力 仲要煩生活<br />\n記住 俾佢地講兩句係冇成本 同佢地鬥長命就得"},{"pid":"49ca24f3bfeb5eed52a5d86877d4bc96c4d24e18","tid":1272034,"uid":271234,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:26:04.000Z","msg":"轉載 Bob叔頻道既一位仁兄留言如下:<br />\n<br />\n奉勸睇開呢個頻道嘅年輕人，同屋企人食飯千祈唔好講政治。就算老人家幾老屎忽都好，你&ldquo;哦哦&rdquo;兩句輕輕帶過就算。<br />\n<br />\n您家兩老，年紀大，腦容量有限。後生嗰時為咗養大你駁命搵食，可能就因為咁而較少時間開拓腦潛能，而令條慧根塞塞哋。<br />\n<br />\n所以有啲媒體、有啲權力機構會利用其影響力去慢慢洗啲老人家腦，貪佢哋夠&ldquo;機能簡單容易install&rdquo;。嚟達到佢哋嘅政治目的。當然，民主或本土派都會咁做，唔單止建制。<br />\n<br />\n所以點解我話唔好同佢哋辯論？其實你好聰明，都唔洗我呢啲老屎忽教喇掛。"},{"pid":"40a05d52efe83c6498675bdad4d52c79e93ca254",