地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:06:13.000Z","msg":"你石頭爆出黎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"又有和理非要求大家孝敬唔尊重生命良知自由既廢老<br />\n<br />\n佢生得你出黎, 又一手搞臭個生存環境, 咁生黎做乜? 扑野既副作用定因為想感受做父母既樂趣所以要生仔出黎受苦?"},{"pid":"889d92c6a3dfa196337d49cbce2f87cce4e59c21","tid":1272034,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dd173945ca41726ebd8739efe20efce9096f014","tid":1272034,"uid":6548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"放心 佢地最怕冇仔送終 佢地一定會受返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好依家有幾多資源拎幾多<br />\n大過有錢搬走唔比家用 等佢地冇錢送終"},{"pid":"d972bd8cd67e24bc7c5d170eee2ac5deeb64cbb4","tid":1272034,"uid":125027,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"01be5a98a99be5ad23f76f32143a886cf83c3873","tid":1272034,"uid":218002,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:18:07.000Z","msg":"借個位放下負<br />\n岩岩同老母嘈完都好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢仲話我無良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為左政治同佢嘈<br />\n我已經為左唔同佢嘈味住良心唔去遊行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就黎出去做野 第日移民咪得 <br />\n唔洗逼到自己咁辛苦<br />\n但有無人明白戈種唔捨得屋企變成咁既心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但出左黎做野一樣都係比人揸住個春袋<br />\n乞食科grad出黎皮幾一個月，想搬又搬唔到，日日打完份牛工番到屋企被迫聽佢地講d好難聽既野，嘈咩最後都係 你仲係食緊我賺番黎既米住緊我層樓。(有比家用)<br />\n今日佢地屌到咩咁真係唔想嘈冇出到去，真係出左就屋企都冇得番，好佩服個個可以炒大獲之後好灑脫咁走出屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日諗有咩辦法可以移民，同佢地日日講外國d樓平d空氣又好岩退休潛移默化佢地。<br />\n但今日真係開始覺得根本唔值得帶佢地移走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a358c5b5b10451b5de673b97682471d50de01755","tid":1272034,"uid":141985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:17:47.000Z","msg":"啱啱同成屋人嘈完（全家十人得我反送中）<br />\n根本講乜佢地都聽唔入耳<br />\n一味係咁話我地搗亂 暴力<br />\n個個去玩 無曬性<br />\n又話條例唔會影響其他人 （解釋又唔聽）<br />\n講乜國有國法 家有家規<br />\n話如果我唔滿意可以離開<br />\n最後spin去明日大愚計劃先收佢地皮<br />\n之後話煮飯有野做就散咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842db9b919f9d26cb85be7c51955a25b8ed8d726","tid":1272034,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"現代卧身嚐膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7735c224da55d90c6b667b9002c69cc1317f8015","tid":1272034,"uid":71860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"入到呢個post真係放鬆左d<br />\n我屋企人又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講過幾次無聲出一陣又打回原形<br />\n已經無力再講 廢時理佢地"},{"pid":"20be17141139bc6100d7066b96313de0619a49c4","tid":1272034,"uid":208486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:22:37.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e60fbee5f6e2a81afecdc35f5b6d3c942d96a5f","tid":1272034,"uid":91336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"支持樓主!"},{"pid":"f5d2b987ae8cf05ef046b3b6dcdf76c1172170a2","tid":1272034,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7735c224da55d90c6b667b9002c69cc1317f8015","tid":1272034,"uid":71860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"入到呢個post真係放鬆左d<br />\n我屋企人又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講過幾次無聲出一陣又打回原形<br />\n已經無力再講 廢時理佢地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11: